name: The Spiritual World1 : Animalas vol.6
description:
Everything that surrounds us comes from points, even the wind. These dots form the image. If we can change the distance of our life points, many things will be easier to understand.
My understanding of these points is a little short but difficult. My sense of these points is the raw material for the formation of anything.
